https://adoptium.net/es/temurin/releases/?version=18 -- JDK used for the project, which is the one suggested for libGDX, use 18.0.2 version with respective architecture for your OS (x64)
https://libgdx.com/wiki/managing-your-assets -- How to manage your assets in bulk with libGDX
https://libgdx.com/wiki/graphics/viewports -- This will be necessary for a better understanding of the code
https://github.com/kotcrab/vis-ui -- UI extension for GDX
https://github.com/czyzby/gdx-skins -- Some skins for the UI
https://www.gamedevelopment.blog/full-libgdx-game-tutorial-menu-control/ -- general purpose tutorial for libGDX creations
